               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Prisoner Campbell. Consider our long confinement, the woman has sworn our lives away.</p>
               <p>Prisoner Thompson. Our lives are sworn away for the sake of the money.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. 
